Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.21,0:00:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就是我夢想的第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早，這是個美妙的好早晨喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再5分鐘…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不～行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，快起來快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要睡到什麼時候啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上的打掃工作要開始了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的每天早上\N都得打掃一個小時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.38,0:01:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.19,0:01:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.25,0:01:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了第一天上課日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.49,0:01:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們班上課挺嚴格的，妳覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.06,0:01:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:45.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.42,0:01:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:02:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步你看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.80,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第5話 學園與制服與我{\fnMS Mincho\fs22}?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.05,0:03:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您指導我們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦，突然跑來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果能事先通知的話\N對我們比較方便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，這城市有電話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.88,0:03:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊，留下這麼多科學技術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊就是珊瑚星組的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說的是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.79,0:04:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像賣到叫“後台”的那家店去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們好像很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們先離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感想如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完～全～跟不上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.55,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一堂是體育課
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.95,0:04:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該很擅長體育吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有記得帶體育服來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.43,0:04:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我好像忘了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩帆姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個捲捲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.49,0:04:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.82,0:05:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡同學\N妳怎麼會做出那種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳跟我來一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…幹嘛，做什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳的制服吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得我好像忘了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，還勞煩妳們特地送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？怎麼會？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別演這種無聊的戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳把這件制服賣到\N叫做“後台”的可疑店家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑…是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您應該知道乙HiME在許多國家\N是許多人幢憬的對象很受歡迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後台就是\N專為乙HiME迷們經營的店家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:06:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以愛莉卡的制服\N被送到那裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得在某些狂熱者之間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這類商品…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的制服和體育服一類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說可以賣到相當高價
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那應該不是她做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看她似乎出身邊境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不知道制服可以拿來賣錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出身邊境啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫愛莉卡的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何國家在背後挺她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.17,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也沒有依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我來當她的金主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這樣不太妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她舞鬥的能力挺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想\N她成為Meister的可能性蠻低的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你這麼說的話\N那就不要勉強好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.30,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳對學姊講話怎麼這麼沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用作弊的方式入學就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳的學費還沒著落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，為什麼我要被妳訓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們珍珠前三名叫做三和弦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須負責指導學生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我問妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天這件制服在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.44,0:07:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為昨晚弄髒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來想拿去洗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻忘在洗衣間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.28,0:07:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一聽就知道是扯謊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是很窮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我絕對沒有做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼這個\N會跑到那種店去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳想說有人想害妳\N而把它偷走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這種\N沒有後盾又沒有依靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.92,0:08:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不適合這間學園又礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事情交給我們處理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以比妳們\N更公平審慎地判斷事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.04,0:08:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不服氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看看這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.68,0:08:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位匿名人士說要資助妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說以前受過令堂關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要接受由妳決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣妳應該就不會\N再受到莫名其妙的質疑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會受到中傷了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡·夢宮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.65,0:09:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且不論買賣一事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有管理好制服而導致遺失\N確實是妳的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳應該明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼在事實明朗化之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.79,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳在宿舍反省
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可以到教室上課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡賣制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後聽說\N剛才被詩帆姊姊帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.44,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是我記得昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像有說\N想要找個好賺錢的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她剛入學\N畢竟也是我們的同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們當然要相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.33,0:09:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下…真是大事一樁了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要太在意那個叫愛莉卡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定很快就會被搞垮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:09:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是她被退學而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嚴厲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小不點？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是賣掉制服還是什麼的\N引起一陣軒然大波呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不能待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王，您要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說，學園啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做完這些之前\N我不會讓妳踏出去一步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩有點可憐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看她過去應該\N沒有被惡意對待過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在盡三和弦的職責而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括這個部分在內呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以茜，該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我們的立場來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.84,0:10:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前受到令堂非常多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望能夠替妳\N盡微薄之力以報答她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用介意還款事宜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我協助妳完成夢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈禱妳能夠成為\N跟令堂一樣出色的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…我可以相信這個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳難道想說有人想害妳\N而把它偷走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像妳這種\N沒有後台又沒有依靠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.15,0:11:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不適合這間學園又礙眼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被討厭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次正式到學校上學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常期待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.29,0:11:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不該來這裡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.00,0:12:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就立刻出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為妳是\N無論如何都想成為乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才冒險跟我舞鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳也只是這點程度罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會毀掉熬過嚴格訓練\N才能進這學校就讀的妮娜的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的夢想真的有這個價值嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我好不容易找到的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算是亂來也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要拼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯，依琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，我很擔心妳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有賣制服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想知道\N為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳們，幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.58,0:13:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也能幫點忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畏畏縮縮畏畏縮縮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她那是什麼態度嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈緒學姊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是搞不過妳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是怎麼啦？突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出許可？妳們也要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，茜姊姊已經批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果珍珠第一名的她\N願意負責的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.50,0:13:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要東張西望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不但沒有乖乖反省\N還是違規外出耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MP4的最新款耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們是茜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姊姊有事情抽不開身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是茜的朋友\N我叫和也·克勞捷克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.41,0:14:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是溫德布倫大學2年級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…是男人拿來賣掉的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人說是自己撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店員說第一次看到那個客人\N所以不太記得長相
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，關於制服的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是店員將破掉的地方\N縫補起來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很髒，所以還洗過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還說其實不要洗比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有說“又來了”喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說除了我們之外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有人跑來問相同的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為多了一份臨時收入啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是檢到好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個啊，這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你挺闊綽的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝的制服\N真的這麼好賣啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.52,0:15:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在我們的地盤上搶生意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為可以全身而退嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱麗葉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.90,0:15:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常謝謝你\N麻煩你這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是茜拜託我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.24,0:15:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次去那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識到不少東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:15:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子不對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME的幼苗\N竟然跟男人約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.50,0:16:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王少校午安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，埃爾斯汀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.84,0:16:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝妳們平時常照顧妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得看妳這麼沒精神呢，螞蟻仔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，聽說妳因為\N繳不出學費而賣制服？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我聽說\N妳確實沒有後盾也沒有依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人會好好幫助我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪來的怪胎啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定跟你不一樣\N是個體貼又帥氣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罷，妳好好唸書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以兔那個人後梅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒幫上什麼忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.12,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了，這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟要從會進出\N那種地方的人身上問出情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得有幾分技巧才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看妳才剛入學沒多久\N就搞出不小的花樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳特地跑來說這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我就是來笑妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白女王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.55,0:17:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了，讓命也看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠上哪去啦？快帶牠來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻貓的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那條手帕…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.78,0:17:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來，昨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎底揭曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒犯，是陛下的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:17:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.63,0:18:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚餐的時候\N愛莉卡的制服上面沾到鴇羽菇湯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而巴拿出來\N擦衣服的手帕上面也沾到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這條手帕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命很喜歡鴇羽菇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命找到愛莉卡放在洗衣間的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在帶回家的途中弄掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:27.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是妳的幻想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服上裂開來的痕跡就是鐵證
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠如各位所見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.37,0:18:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條手帕也是以同樣方式\N產生相同的裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊大概是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命每次要回迎賓館時\N所使用的路徑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢到制服的男子就把它賣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟制服和賣掉制服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓根是兩件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是本案的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事，陛下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是栽贓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命才不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是栽贓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們這些沒禮貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是栽贓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼愛莉卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場騷動的後續
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會交給陛下處理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這麼一來各位也能理解\N我沒有賣制服了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也交到願意相信我\N幫助我的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我打算相信寫信來的這個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.93,0:19:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是本案的前因後果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.40,0:19:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.01,0:19:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那隻貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的是哪個人造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.21,0:20:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才問題多多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很謝謝妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.25,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依琳娜，埃爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁想道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.63,0:20:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒有為妳做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不打算為妳做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.24,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有點對不起真白女王和命呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢，當作一件事情的收尾\N差不多就是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果因為這點小事就害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.45,0:20:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以後還是別再做了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那種男人有來往
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒黴的是妳自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這種卑劣的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳還想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我絕對不會輕饒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是場鬧劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光憑那種破綻百出的推理…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪莉亞女士，別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件匿名援助的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會稍嫌過早嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在關於愛莉卡的身世之謎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.31,0:21:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,線索只有這個人和蒼天的青玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是善加利用\N可以利用的東西罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.29,0:21:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管那個人有什麼意圖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過把它撕爛\N然後放在她桌上吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這是做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.74,0:21:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想賺零用錢是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為這樣可以鬧比較大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要撕毀制服有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.71,0:21:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.11,0:21:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會做好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.40,0:22:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.69,0:22:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.67,0:23:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.48,0:23:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個香菇湯好好暍呢\N（妮娜，被捲了…orz)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴇羽菇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有波菇目貓座科\N俗稱“舞衣”菇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.75,0:23:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲，竟然連蕈類都…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.98,0:23:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還算幸運的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.40,0:00:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
